CYCLE :-
========

  => by default sequence created with NOCYCLE.

  => if sequence is NOCYCLE then it starts from start with and generates upto max and
       after reaching max then it stops.

 => if sequence is CYCLE then it starts from start with and generates upto max and 
       after reaching max then it will reset to min.

  CREATE SEQUENCE S10
  START WITH 1
  INCREMENT BY 1
  MAXVALUE 5
  MINVALUE 1
  CYCLE 
  CACHE 4 ;


 SQL>SELECT S10.NEXTVAL FROM DUAL ; 
 

